'''Microsoft Band'''，是一款由[[微軟|微軟]]開發與設計，帶有[[健身|健身]]手環功能的[[智能手表|智能手表]]，並於2014年10月29日，在[[美國|美國]]發售了限量版<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://twitter.com/Microsoft/status/527651861810413568|title = Introducing Microsoft Band|date = 2014-10-29|accessdate = 2014-10-30|website = [[Twitter|Twitter]]|publisher = [[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|last = |first = |archive-date = 2020-12-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201214140629/https://twitter.com/Microsoft/status/527651861810413568|dead-url = no}}</ref>，售價199[[美元|美元]]。Microsoft Band於網上販售時便已供不應求，在美國的大部分地區被搶購一空。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url = http://news.softpedia.com/news/Microsoft-Launches-Band-Smartwatch-Wannabe-for-Windows-Phone-iOS-and-Android-463504.shtml|title = Microsoft Launches Band, Smartwatch Wannabe for Windows Phone, iOS, and Android|date = 2014-10-30|accessdate = 2014-10-30|website = [[Softpedia|Softpedia]]|publisher = |last = Popa|first = Bogdan|archive-date = 2021-01-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210110001237/https://news.softpedia.com/news/Microsoft-Launches-Band-Smartwatch-Wannabe-for-Windows-Phone-iOS-and-Android-463504.shtml|dead-url = no}}</ref>

這個手錶內含10個[[传感器|传感器]]，一個[[光学|光学]]{{link-en|心率錶|heart rate monitor}}，{{link-en|GPS導航裝置|GPS navigation device}}，和[[紫外线|紫外线]]传感器，<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.pcworld.com/article/2840978/microsoft-enters-smartwatch-market-with-200-microsoft-band.html|title = Meet Microsoft Band, Microsoft's $200, fitness-focused smartwatch|date = 2014-10-29|accessdate = 2014-10-30|website = 《[[PC_World雜誌|PC World雜誌]]》|last = Hachman|first = Mark|archive-date = 2021-01-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210110001246/https://www.pcworld.com/article/2840978/microsoft-enters-smartwatch-market-with-200-microsoft-band.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>[[電池|電池]]在充滿電後能連續使用兩天。<ref name=":0" /> 這個裝置的一部份功能依賴於它的配套[[APP|APP]][[Microsoft_Health|Microsoft Health]]，適用於[[Windows_Phone_8.1|Windows Phone 8.1]]、[[Android|Android 4.3+]]，和[[iOS|iOS 7.1+]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.microsoft.com/microsoft-band/en-us/support/hardware/system-requirements|title = System requirements for Microsoft Band|date = |accessdate = 2014-10-31|website = |publisher = [[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|last = |first = |deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141102005742/http://www.microsoft.com/microsoft-band/en-us/support/hardware/system-requirements|archivedate = 2014-11-02}}</ref>。

它內建的[[應用程式|應用程式]]稱為「磁貼」（Tiles），例如有[[體能鍛煉|體能鍛煉]]、紫外线、警鈴與定時器、來電、[[簡訊|簡訊]]、[[日曆|日曆]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]、[[氣象|氣象]]等<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.microsoft.com/microsoft-band/en-us/support/tiles|title = The tiles on your Microsoft Band|date = |accessdate = 2014-10-30|website = |publisher = [[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|last = |first = |archive-date = 2016-08-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160818085707/http://www.microsoft.com/microsoft-band/en-us/support/tiles|dead-url = no}}</ref>；如果搭配使用Windows Phone 8.1的裝置，還能啟用[[Microsoft_Cortana|Cortana]]（某些功能仍然必須使用手機才能執行）<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.microsoft.com/Microsoft-Band/en-us/support/tiles/using-cortana|title = Use Cortana with Microsoft Band and your Windows Phone|date = |accessdate = 2014-10-30|website = |publisher = [[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|last = |first = |archive-date = 2016-08-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160828033942/http://www.microsoft.com/microsoft-band/en-us/support/tiles/using-cortana|dead-url = no}}</ref> 。

用戶可從手機查看來自通知中心磁貼（Notifications Center Tile）的最新通告消息，這個功能也是促銷微軟的軟體和授權許可給開發者和[[OEM|代工商]]的途徑之一。 <ref name=WPCentral>{{cite news|last=Rubino|first=Daniel|title=Why Microsoft Band is in short supply (it's not a marketing conspiracy)|url=http://www.windowscentral.com/why-microsoft-band-short-supply|newspaper=WPCentral|date=2014-11-01|accessdate=2014-11-14|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110001302/https://www.windowscentral.com/why-microsoft-band-short-supply|dead-url=no}}</ref>

